<div class="section" id="documentation">
<h1>Documentation</h1>
<p><a class="reference external" href="fityk-manual.html">The manual</a>
(<a class="reference external" href="http://www.unipress.waw.pl/fityk/fityk-manual.pdf">PDF</a>)
documents mainly commands of the fityk mini-language.</p>
<p><a class="reference external" href="http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/fityk/">Trac Wiki</a>
contains all other informations.
You are welcome to contribute.</p>
<p>Citing fityk in academic papers:
M. Wojdyr,
<a class="reference external" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1107/S0021889810030499">J. Appl. Cryst. 43, 1126-1128</a>
(2010)
[<a class="reference external" href="http://www.unipress.waw.pl/fityk/fityk-JAC-10-reprint.pdf">reprint</a>]</p>
</div>
<div class="section" id="questions">
<h1>Questions?</h1>
<p>Join the Google group
<a class="reference external" href="http://groups.google.com/group/fityk-users/">fityk-users</a>.
You may select option &#8220;no mail&#8221; and use the web interface to send messages.
Feel free to send questions, comments, bug reports, new feature requests
and success stories.</p>
<p>Asking for a new feature usually results in adding the request to
the <a class="reference external" href="http://fityk.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/fityk/trunk/TODO">TODO list</a>
or, if it already is in the list, in assigning higher priority to it.</p>
<p>If for some reasons you do not want to use the group,
you may contact directly the maintainer of the program:
<a class="reference external" href="http://www.unipress.waw.pl/~wojdyr/">Marcin Wojdyr</a>  <a class="reference external" href="mailto:wojdyr&#37;&#52;&#48;gmail&#46;com">wojdyr<span>&#64;</span>gmail<span>&#46;</span>com</a>.</p>
